title: Give yourself permission to be creative | Ethan Hawke
itunes:author: Ethan Hawke
description: Reflecting on moments that shaped his life, actor Ethan Hawke examines how courageous expression promotes healing and connection with one another -- and invites you to discover your own unabashed creativity. "There is no path till you walk it," he says.
